          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "HPGE"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The HPGe detector (Canberra GAMMA-X with",
                "20.7% relative efficiency) used for determining the",
                "activity was calibrated using 57Co, 60Co, 137Cs and",
                "152Eu point sources."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ERR-ANALYS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": "ERR-T",
                "minimum_value": null,
                "maximum_value": null,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " The main contribution to the uncertainty",
                " (one standard deviation) inthe cross-section values",
                "comes from the following sources:"
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": "ERR-1",
                "minimum_value": null,
                "maximum_value": null,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " the beam intensity (5%),"
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": "ERR-2",
                "minimum_value": null,
                "maximum_value": null,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " number of target atomsin the beam (5%),",
                "  * HPGe efficiency calibration (3-6%, depending on the",
                "                                     energy) and",
                "  * the peak-areafitting (0.5-8%).",
                "UniSAMPO- Shaman analysis package reports the activity",
                "of the nuclide and itsuncertainty at the end of the",
                "irradiation. This reported uncertainty includes the",
                "uncertaintiesof the efficiency calibration,",
                "peak-area fitting, the decay data and the half-life.",
                "Therefore,the estimated uncertainty of the",
                "cross-section values was obtained by adding the",
                "activity uncertainty from UniSAMPO-Shaman to the",
                "beam-intensity and target-thickness uncertainties."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": "EN-ERR",
                "minimum_value": null,
                "maximum_value": null,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " uncertainty in the energy"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The authors noted that at these energies the",
                "recommended values of IAEA (IAEA-TECDOC-1211,2001)",
                "for Zn-62 were significantly lower. Also, measured",
                "results (for Zn-62) were some what lower than the IAEA",
                "present recommended values (see Website:",
                "                   http://www-nds.iaea.org/medical/)"
              ]
            }
